OL,3,CYoung driver and two passengers died
OL,4,Cafter he 'lost control of car and hit
OL,5,Ctree'
OL,7,FA teenager from Wrexham who had his
OL,8,Fdriving licence for less than six
OL,9,Fmonths was killed alongside two
OL,10,Ffriends after losing control of his
OL,11,Fcar on a bridge and crashing into a
OL,12,Ftree, an inquest has heard.
OL,14,FDafydd Huw Craven-Jones, 18, Morgan
OL,15,FJones, 17, and Sophie Bates, 17, died
OL,16,Fand Brooke Varley, also 17 at the
OL,17,Ftime, survived after Dafydd lost
OL,18,Fcontrol of his Ford Ka on a humpback
OL,19,Fbridge in Penkridge, Staffordshire, at
OL,20,F11.47pm on 25 May last year.
