OL,7,FThe driver, Dafydd Huw Craven-Jones,
OL,8,Fwho had passed his test at the end of
OL,9,FNovember 2023, had taken a video of
OL,10,Fhimself as he went to pick up his
OL,11,Fthree friends from a house party
OL,12,Fsaying he feared he had been caught
OL,13,Fspeeding at 90mph on a 70mph road.
OL,15,FNeither Sophie, from Stafford, nor
OL,16,FBrooke, from Newport in Shropshire,
OL,17,Fwere wearing seatbelts at the time of
OL,18,Fthe collision on the 60mph road.
