OL,7,FIn a statement read out at the
OL,8,Fcoroners court, Brooke described a
OL,9,F"rollercoaster feeling in my tummy"
OL,10,Fbefore the car swerved and she blacked
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FShe had also felt "scared" that Dafydd
OL,14,Fwas driving too fast and had asked him
OL,15,Fto slow down.
