OL,5,Ctree'
OL,7,FIn a statement read out at the
OL,8,Finquest, Dafydd's mother Paula Craven-
OL,9,FJones said she had been in the car
OL,10,Fwith her son on a number of occasions
OL,11,Fsince he passed his test and had no
OL,12,Fconcerns about his driving ability.
OL,14,FDafydd had no drink or drugs in his
OL,15,Fsystem and there is no evidence that
OL,16,Fhe was using his phone at the time of
OL,17,Fthe collision, Sergeant Richard Moors
OL,18,Ffrom Staffordshire Police said.
