OL,7,FHis car had been correctly insured and
OL,8,Fhe had a full MOT, and there were no
OL,9,Fdefects with the vehicle that
OL,10,Fcontributed to the crash, he added.
OL,12,FRecording their deaths as being the
OL,13,Fresult of a road traffic collision, Ms
OL,14,FDixon said: "Dafydd suffered a loss of
OL,15,Fcontrol, mounting the nearside verge
OL,16,Fbefore travelling to the opposite side
OL,17,Fof the road, colliding with an
OL,18,Festablished tree. The driver's side
OL,19,Fseat had been struck from behind by a
OL,20,Frear seat passenger who wasn't wearing
OL,21,Fa seatbelt.
